<ion-view title="Review Fare &amp; Purchase" id="page4">
    <ion-content padding="false" class="has-header" style='background-color:#fafafa;'>
        <div class="info-container" style="background-color:white;">
            <div class="row content-padding">
                <div class="col-20 col-center">
                    <i class="ion-card" style="font-size:40px"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="col-80">
                    <p style="color:#3097f3">{{card}}</p>
                    <p>MasterCard</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class='info-container' style='padding:15px;'>
            <h4>{{flightDetails.origin}} to {{flightDetails.destination}}</h4>
            <p>{{tripType['description']}}</p>
            <p>{{tripDetails.departureDate | date:'MMM d, yyyy'}} - {{tripDetails.returnDate | date:'MMM d, yyyy'}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row content-padding" ng-repeat="traveller in savedTravellers">
            <div class="col">
                <p>{{traveller.firstName}} {{traveller.lastName}}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col align-right">
                <p>{{flightList.tierPrice | currency:"$":0 }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row content-padding">
            <div class="col">
                <h4>Total</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="col align-right">
                <h4>{{totalCost | currency:"$":0}}</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <div class='row'>
            <div class='col'>
                <p style='text-align:center;'><a ng-click='openFaqModal()' style='color:#3097f3'>Frequently Asked Questions</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </ion-content>
    <button id="reviewFarePurchase-button5" ng-click="confirmation()" style="border-radius:0px 0px 0px 0px;" class="button button-positive button-block fixed-to-bottom">Pay Securely Now</button>

    <script id="confirmation.html" type="text/ng-template">
        <ion-modal-view>
            <ion-content>
                <div class='confirmation-container'>
                    <div class='confirmation-content'>
                        <h2>Pack your bags!</h2>
                        <h4>A confirmation email will be sent shortly.</h4>
                        <br>
                        <i class='icon ion-checkmark-circled'></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </ion-content>
          </ion-modal-view>
    </script>

    <script id="faq.html" type="text/ng-template">
        <ion-modal-view>
            <ion-header-bar>
                <i style='font-size:20px;padding:5px;' ng-click="faqModal.hide()" class='ion-close'></i>
            </ion-header-bar>
                <ion-content>
                    <div class='info-container'>
                        <h3 class='align-center'>FAQs</h3>
                        <h4>If I pay the price shown now, when will I actually receive my flight confirmation and details?</h4>
                        <p>You will receive a Hopper receipt immediately with a Hopper Booking Confirmation Number. You will then receive your flight confirmation and details at least a month before your departure date.</p>
                        <br>
                        <h4>Can I get a full refund if I cancel at any point before I receive my flight confirmation?</h4>
                        <p>Yes! Your Timewarp Fare is fully changeable and refundable until your flights are finalized and then for 24 hours afterwards.</p>
                        <br>
                        <h4>How can you guarentee this price?</h4>
                        <p>Using our prediction algorithm, we are able to accurately predict the future prices of flights. We know that buying flights is typically the first step of planning a trip, so we wanted allow you to buy them immediately while still being able to take advantage of our predictions! If our predictions end up being wrong, we will pay the extra cost. Your flights and this price are 100% guarateed.</p>
                        <br>
                    </div>
                </ion-content>
          </ion-modal-view>
    </script>
</ion-view>

